      430.31
    ],
    "text": "2.Section 6 of the Buddhist Cultural Centre of Nedimala,Dehiwala (Incorporation) Act, No. 30 of 2008 is herebyamended by the repeal of paragraph (b) thereof and thesubstitution therefor of the following :\u2014",
